# 11. Pascal's Triangle

```java
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int n = 5;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int num = 1;

            for (int j = 0; j <= i; j++) {
                System.out.print(num + " ");
                num = num * (i - j) / (j + 1);
            }

            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
```

Output:

```
1
1 1
1 2 1
1 3 3 1
1 4 6 4 1
```

